    <p>Here is every tier we could verify, sequenced from free to the highest reported one-time price. Treat every number below as directional rather than fixed — every product review on this site already flags OLSP pricing as promotion-sensitive and prone to change across platform relaunches, and this guide inherits that same caution.</p>

    <div class="table-scroll">
    <table>
